May the spirit of giving remain with us all year, not just in its final months. So today I’d like to talk about Sarah’s Home again. Sarah's Home is a faith-based residential home on the front range of Colorado for girls age 12 up to 18 who have been rescued from human trafficking. They are licensed as a specialized group home through the state of Colorado.

Trafficking survivors experience trauma that affects their whole being. Because of this, Sarah’s Home works to bring healing to mind, body, and spirit. Their program consists of counseling and therapy, life skill training, medical care, job skill training, spiritual guidance, relationship training, mentoring and education. Recently, they expended their services to provide the same for male survivors - Daniel’s Academy.
👉🏻For more information about Sarah’s Home: https://www.sarahshome.us/

✨EVERY PENNY COUNTS✨ - To DONATE to this local Colorado organization trying to help as many as they can: https://www.sarahshome.us/give

⛷️ I’m so proud of them!!!! John and the kids all had their first private ski lesson this past weekend  at @monarchmountain! The goal was for them to be able to stop and turn at the end of the lesson/day 1 and then we could spend day 2 on greens adjusting to the mountain. AND ALL OF THEM DID IT!!! I swung by and went up the magic carpet at the end of their lesson and watched as each one made it down the bunny hill, in control! Shout out to Jim for being an excellent ski instructor!!!👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻

I grew up skiing and hadn’t been on the mountain in 20 years!!! I dropped them at ski school, said a prayer, and headed off on my own to find my legs. I knew I missed skiing but I didn’t realize how much! I spent hours by myself and found may back to the black diamonds.👏🏻👏🏻🙌🏻

Skiing in Colorado is unlike anything else!!! I cannot believe I get to call this place home!😭😭🙏🏻

As for our next trip… we’re headed back again this weekend. Cheers to the mountains 🏔️⛷️

That moment when you drop your whole family off at private lessons and head out on the mountain alone.💞⛷️🏔️🙌🏻
#ski #monarchmountain #colorado #coloradolife #coloradogirl
Just Colorado…showing off again….💞🏔️😍 #colorado #coloradolife #monument #nofilter
⛷️ Last Saturday they learned how to ski. Yesterday they skied this @monarchmountain …and didn’t fall.👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻😭👏🏻👏🏻 #soproud #SkiMonarch #blackdiamond

👉🏻He also does a lot of work to support pediatric cancer. Don’t judge a book by its cover.
